Bring 8 cups water to a boil. Pour over tea bags into large heat resistant bowl; cover and steep 5 minutes. Remove tea bags, squeezing gently. Stir in SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, orange juice, and lemon juice. Combine 4 cups water, cinnamon sticks and cloves in a small saucepan; bring to a boil, cover, and simmer 20 minutes. Pour mixture through a wire-mesh strainer into tea mixture, discarding spices. Pour into mugs and serve tea hot with lemon and orange slices, whole cloves and cinnamon sticks.